entry.content: Replying to @OmManiPadmi How is race a nom-sequitor when the question asked abouy race? The logic is both class and racial discrimination exist. If a person doesn't want an inference drawn that people are inferior on the basis of class, they should not make an argument that certain people are inferior on the basis of race, which is what the commenter was doing.
